  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Right now, the game only includes the first episode of <i>Vanova's Stories</i>. But this first case is just the beginning… More episodes are on the way in free future updates!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/21f0e51b0f5239d44e7e93c2bf83e04a.poster.avif?t=1747090428\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/21f0e51b0f5239d44e7e93c2bf83e04a.webm?t=1747090428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/21f0e51b0f5239d44e7e93c2bf83e04a.mp4?t=1747090428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Halfway between a board game and a video game, Vanova's Stories is an investigative adventure for 2 to 4 players. Do you like wacky, colorful worlds, cooperating with your friends, and narrative point-and-clicks? Then this game is for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/07e6f28c8b1b60d4bbe5b120d38c94bf.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>Discover a hand-drawn world and explore the city of Vanova to find clues about the committed crimes. Whether in 2D or 3D, your observational skills will be your greatest assets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/e962f95dfe94ab5d5eefd88dc413c774.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>Each location you investigate includes a number of unusual and eccentric characters. Some may refuse to talk to you... Perhaps your teammates will have better luck?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/16360b8da68d6200ad5b2a14f5ee9238.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>Agility, intimidation, strength, charm—everyone has their own unique ability that will lead them to clues only they can uncover. Your adventure and dialogue options will vary depending on your detective, so choose wisely! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/7cfa6849adef400c4f837cbfab66939b.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>A suspect is refusing to talk to you, and you want to show him evidence to get him to confess? Swap clues with a teammate and get them to do it for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/698a53050fc03c850e326b60f1b4e6d0.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>Different investigations require different approaches. Each one will feature a new mechanic, forcing you to rethink the way you investigate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/1e7353a5568805f1a62c765825acf063.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>Think you've discovered the truth? Get together with your friends and tell your boss what you've found, linking all the pieces together. Make sure everyone agrees, as a wrong hypothesis could cost you dearly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/29d47d73e26bcf5736b1a2b9d016d5cd.avif?t=1747090428\" width=622 height=329 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Right now, the game only includes the first episode of <i>Vanova's Stories</i>. But this first case is just the beginning… More episodes are on the way in free future updates!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/21f0e51b0f5239d44e7e93c2bf83e04a.poster.avif?t=1747090428\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/21f0e51b0f5239d44e7e93c2bf83e04a.webm?t=1747090428\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/21f0e51b0f5239d44e7e93c2bf83e04a.mp4?t=1747090428\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Halfway between a board game and a video game, Vanova's Stories is an investigative adventure for 2 to 4 players. Do you like wacky, colorful worlds, cooperating with your friends, and narrative point-and-clicks? Then this game is for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/07e6f28c8b1b60d4bbe5b120d38c94bf.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>Discover a hand-drawn world and explore the city of Vanova to find clues about the committed crimes. Whether in 2D or 3D, your observational skills will be your greatest assets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/e962f95dfe94ab5d5eefd88dc413c774.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>Each location you investigate includes a number of unusual and eccentric characters. Some may refuse to talk to you... Perhaps your teammates will have better luck?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/16360b8da68d6200ad5b2a14f5ee9238.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>Agility, intimidation, strength, charm—everyone has their own unique ability that will lead them to clues only they can uncover. Your adventure and dialogue options will vary depending on your detective, so choose wisely! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/7cfa6849adef400c4f837cbfab66939b.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>A suspect is refusing to talk to you, and you want to show him evidence to get him to confess? Swap clues with a teammate and get them to do it for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/698a53050fc03c850e326b60f1b4e6d0.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>Different investigations require different approaches. Each one will feature a new mechanic, forcing you to rethink the way you investigate.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/1e7353a5568805f1a62c765825acf063.avif?t=1747090428\" width=615 height=146 /></span>Think you've discovered the truth? Get together with your friends and tell your boss what you've found, linking all the pieces together. Make sure everyone agrees, as a wrong hypothesis could cost you dearly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369640/extras/29d47d73e26bcf5736b1a2b9d016d5cd.avif?t=1747090428\" width=622 height=329 /></span></p>",
